result.title: OrderOne
result.content: Hello Codeforces! Few time ago a started learning android developing and as an experience started a writing mobile application that will help competitive programming students to raise up their programming skills.App consists of 3 function: 1)Block that selects the tasks for your level of programming. 2)Contest calendar — you can see further contests in programming from different sites. 3)Explor block — search problems by category. App is aviable by link : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.order.sony.orderone. Thank you for your attention!)
